     # 7. User should be able to click on Visual Editor and see the editor text-bar displays on top of the message box.
     @dispayMessage
    Scenario: User should be able to click on Visual Editor
    When user should be able to click on Visual Editor
      Then user should click Visual Editor
      Then user should be able to see the editor text-bar displays
      Then user should be able to see the editor text-bar displays on top of the message box.

     #8. User should be able to click on the Topic icon to see the Message Topic text box displays on top of the message box.
     @topicIcon
     Scenario: User should be able to click on the Topic icon
       When User should be able to click on the Topic icon
       Then user should be able to click on the Topic icon
       Then user should be able to see the Message Topic
       Then user should be able to see text box displays
       Then user should be able to  see the Message Topic text box displays on top of the message box.



     #9. User should be able to click on "Record Video" tab to record a video and attach it with the message.
       @recordVideo
       Scenario: User should be able to click on "Record Video" tab
       When user login to account succesfully
       Then user should be able to hover over to More Tab and click
       Then user should click Appreciation option
       Then user should be able to click on "Record Video" tab
       Then user should be able to record a video and attach it with with the message


